window.bookSummaryJSON = "<p>To protect those she loves from an unwanted fate, Emie Mercer has returned to the past. Her actions have already created ripples and changed the trajectory of her future. She has gained early access to the system and magic, and is now working with Alliance personnel in an effort to leverage her knowledge of the future to help others.</p> <p>With the aid of her boss and new mentors, Emie will continue to grow and learn, expanding the gap between herself and the rest of the natives of Earth. But by making herself exceptional, she risks the very safety she hoped to create.</p>"; 
